    <briefdescription>
<para>This block executes a command with the std::system() command if a value from a f32vector with a given identifier (symbol) is in a given range. Each index of a vector refers to a identifier. The execution of a command can be blocked for block_time milliseconds after the last execution. </para>
    </briefdescription>
